title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update X USA - Charleston
description:
In this video we will have a look at Charleston (Virginia) which received a photogrammetry update as part of World Update X which has been released earlier this week. We are departing from Yeager airport (KCRW) and make a turn towards the city of Charleston. After our first flyover we will fly over the industry part of the city and make another turn and fly low over the city.
